N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 511.2 - Policy

State Regulations

This Part applies to State actions only. Federally
supported or mandated actions performed by DMNA are not included because these

Federal actions are subject to provisions of the National Environmental Policy

Act of 1969, as implemented by the Department of Defense, and are not
considered to be subject to SEQR. Notes
